reviews.text:
Food- a bit smaller than I imagined, but perfect size for tapas. 
Service - great here, food comes out efficiently as well as drinks 
Drinks- great, as well...

For my first visit, they really knocked it out of the park. 

My friend moved out of town a while ago and was back to visit. We stopped at another place...
On our first night in Columbus, we had a late dinner at Lincoln Social Rooftop. Upon entry, the front staff checked our IDs, including those of my parents....
